title: Jamin Travis -- Of Love and Loss
description: Jamin Travis is an acoustic singer/songwriter who currently resides in Spring Hill, FL. He began playing music at 8 years old and released his first demos of self-written and recorded songs at the age of 15. Since then, his writing and musicianship has grown and it doesn't show any signs of stopping. His first official EP, titled "Of Love and Loss" is now available in CD format and on iTunes, Spotify, Amazon, and more!
